    <title>BIS open data strategy 2012-14</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary/>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sets out the actions BIS will take over the next two years to drive reform and improvement through transparency. Covers datasets that have the potential to create economic opportunities, datasets that are collected in higher and further education. Also looks at providing individuals with access to data about them, satisfaction and experience data, and improving the quality of data published.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
